MOTION DOCKET

01-871. State v. Ahmed.

Belmont C.P. No. 99CR192. This cause is a death penalty appeal from the Court of Common Pleas of Belmont County. Upon consideration of appellant’s motion for reappointment of counsel,

IT IS ORDERED by the court, sua sponte, that appellant’s brief shall be due ninety days from January 9, 2002, and the parties shall otherwise proceed in accordance with S.Ct.Prac.R. XIX(5).
